'''香奈儿蔚蓝'''（Bleu de Chanel）是{{link-en|雅克·波爾格|Jacques Polge}}在2010年为[[香奈儿|香奈儿]]打造的一款男士香水<ref>{{Cite web|title='Bleu de Chanel' channels strength and elegance in new Parfum-strength fragrance|url=https://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/-bleu-de-chanel-channels-strength-and-elegance-in-new-parfum-strength-fragrance,982006.html|accessdate=June 21, 2020|date=May 29, 2018|publisher=Fashion Network}}</ref><ref name="Masterbrand">{{cite web|url=https://wwd.com/fashion-news/textiles/chanel-to-launch-new-men-s-masterbrand-3183600/|title=Chanel To Launch New Men's Masterbrand|last=Naughton|first=Julie|work=Women's Wear Daily|date=July 16, 2010|accessdate=June 21, 2020}}</ref><ref name="FragranticaEDT">{{cite web|url=https://www.fragrantica.com/perfume/Chanel/Bleu-de-Chanel-9099.html|title=Bleu de Chanel cologne – a fragrance for men 2010|publisher=Fragrantica|accessdate=June 21, 2020}}</ref>。最初香奈儿蔚蓝的香水是[[淡香水|淡香水]]，2014年版的香奈儿蔚蓝淡香水是由雅克·波爾格調配<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bleu de Chanel Eau de Parfum Chanel cologne – a fragrance for men 2014|url=https://www.fragrantica.com/perfume/Chanel/Bleu-de-Chanel-Eau-de-Parfum-25967.html|accessdate=June 21, 2020|publisher=Fragrantica}}</ref>，2018年版的香水是由他的儿子{{link-en|奥利维尔·波尔格|Olivier Polge}}調配<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bleu de Chanel Parfum Chanel cologne – a fragrance for men 2018|url=https://www.fragrantica.com/perfume/Chanel/Bleu-de-Chanel-Parfum-49912.html|accessdate=June 21, 2020|publisher=Fragrantica}}</ref>。

